<title>THE HOLY CITY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka hinna hi pakcha bangin,
 Chawmlo kalin bei ina;
 Zana mang khuo a hung vaka,
 A beih kit bang hi ahi.

[V2]
 Aw, ka thagau vanah lengin,
 Lei bang dinga ngai na him?
 Na kumsawt khawpi hawih zuon in,
 Mi thiengthote khawpi chuh.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel hinna hi bang ahim?
 Natna leh lungkhamna mai;
 Kipahna, nawpna cheng cheng hi,
 Hampa, pakcha bang ahi.

[V4]
 3. I guol deihtak chiehsate chu,
 Kipak takin a tung tau;
 Lalchutphah velah la a sau,
 I kumsawt Lal chawian in.

[V5]
 4. A lopina vak hawih tak chuh,
 Ni sangin a vak hawih zawi;
 Ziechun Lopi masang a chun,
 I Lal Isu chuh mui tiu.

[V6]
 5. Ka Aw hawih neihsun cheng chengin,
 Chawian ka ka tun tieng leh;
 Vakhu bangin len thiem leng Aw!
 Leng ingka van gam akhun.
 Aw ka thagau tuhin leng in,
 Khawvel hi taihsan inla;
 Na kumsawt khawpi hawih zuonin,
 Khawpi hawih-Lalpa gam chuh.</lyrics>
</song>